dct_title_s: Syria - Cypern - Palestina - Mesopotamia - Babylonia - zwey Arabia - mit Bergen - Waesseren und Staetten
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography, drainage, boundaries, places of historical interest.
Descriptive text, e.g.: In dieser Tafel sind begriffen di Landtschafften...
Appears in Muenster's Cosmographei Basel, Heinrich Petri, 1545, Map no. XXI. The map is identical with Ptolemy's Tabula IIII Asiae in Muenster's 1540 Ptolemy's edition.
